{"tid":1082651,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"逾六成女性不認同「有樓才結婚」","createTime":"2019-03-29T05:57:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-29T13:02:31.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":29,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"6666979da44d4f487f469039d52b9dec4464a391","tid":1082651,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T05:57:53.000Z","msg":"一項調查顯示，七成男士認為擁有物業容易結識異性，不過有六成半女性不認同置業是結婚的必要條件，更有逾八成人願意與伴侶一起儲蓄置業。<br />\n<br />\n交友配對公司HK Romance Dating於4至6月透過街頭訪問及網上問卷，訪問逾600名市民，調查單身男女對置業、樓市的看法。<br />\n結果顯示，六成男性和六成半女性認為人生必須置業。若有100萬積蓄，三成半男士及過半女士表示，會選付首期。<br />\n<br />\n有61%女士表示，異性擁有私人物業會較吸引，擇偶條件會加分；70%男士認為擁有物業較易識另一半。近半男士認為擁有越大額物業識女朋友機會越大；女士則相反。<br />\n<br />\n不過調查認為沒有物業的男士不用灰心，因為逾八成女士願意同伴侶一齊儲首期買樓，且有65%女性不認同要先買樓後結婚。HK Romance Dating指，有物業並非女士唯一擇偶條件，同樣重視男方有沒有穩定並有效的儲蓄習慣，以及人生規劃。<br />\n<br />\n此外，七成男士及女士期望與心儀對象選購600萬或以下單位。近三成男女受訪者望與心儀對象選購401至500呎單位。逾八成男女認為樓價持續升勢今年內不會置業。<br />\n<br />\n該公司建議，情侶共同儲蓄買樓時，切忌變成「賺錢第一、拍拖第二」，用盡時間去工作賺錢買樓，卻忽略了自己與伴侶相處的時間，單純變成「樓奴」。◇"},{"pid":"743526e3c4cb3f12b4cfc3219b76472ea321f6d9","tid":1082651,"uid":186844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:01:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9721f9ea1c142564924cb6a575380fa5b154b667","tid":1082651,"uid":190540,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:11:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"df0c19c0727e444c67b775ef8ed64ccac0c7ad5d","tid":1082651,"uid":190540,"like":14,"dislike":0,"score":14,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:11:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bda979630b9f4a579d9330b1b5cd32886acfda87","tid":1082651,"uid":11148,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:11:59.000Z","msg":"女人好蠱惑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89648e11c891e075bf66ac3638503dd070ed8089","tid":1082651,"uid":127991,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:16:05.000Z","msg":"有樓先同你拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7283eb1bec516b2f0265db9892d1a4ce7f022870","tid":1082651,"uid":130695,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:16:07.000Z","msg":"緊係啦，陣間比個有錢佬見到<br />\n挑，又係拜金雞點算<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n其實真係好多香港女人肯同你撐<br />\n都係香港大點會唔知香港咩事<br />\n係有人特登醜化哂佢地<br />\n男女都會睇錢講錢<br />\n你無錢話啲女閪鑲金<br />\n掉返轉 你又有冇條金撚引人含<br />\n無就大家收皮 搵個門當戶對算鳩數啦"},{"pid":"ae4b2327497bb1ef83bae53802e06daeaea352e5","tid":1082651,"uid":226254,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:17:43.000Z","msg":"有樓唔一定結 啱呀<br />\n只係無樓一定唔結姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf666bb4b1007677245ff61a82a6dc78206bd91","tid":1082651,"uid":119864,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:17:55.000Z","msg":"冇樓唔緊要，但起碼有錢係手，租到靚樓貴樓<br />\n公屋<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不了<br />\n女人大話連編"},{"pid":"a8a4e71c683f7cc9c81753ffec4340a5bad6ecce","tid":1082651,"uid":22362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:18:32.000Z","msg":"唔同話俾你知我真係好貪錢想做少奶咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7042bc8a18d19afa4958cfbd0bd09208a438e2d7","tid":1082651,"uid":59868,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:18:51.000Z","msg":"逾十成女性認同「不會跟毒撚結婚」"},{"pid":"9115b3c85e3ff5857cb306b27edd67d8659b4b46","tid":1082651,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:19:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過有六成半女性不認同置業是結婚的必要條件</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n不是必要條件<br />\n但好大機會有優先"},{"pid":"4976d45dbdc0357b5e4d15b497d881cc8f4cb188","tid":1082651,"uid":21873,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:23:28.000Z","msg":"起碼有40%表示認同"},{"pid":"27dd3e8929213693db5798f11e05cbe95adb65b3","tid":1082651,"uid":78122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:25:10.000Z","msg":"但唔想同奶奶住"},{"pid":"4ffd5e17bec8537a4d614711ee577a4593598a0a","tid":1082651,"uid":24015,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T06:25:21.000Z","msg":"因為有樓都未必同你結<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"095c346e63d5a0acb5560d9f09629a2afcba0f4a","tid":1082651,"uid":86383,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:48:24.000Z","msg":"我就唔信住公屋瞓碌架床<br />\n仲要冇自己間房都娶到老婆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8ab5d5e2e26d016a06ddd0c2383bc079671eb9f","tid":1082651,"uid":126219,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T08:55:26.000Z","msg":"問卷說不，身體卻很誠實"},{"pid":"4614b575d02871fb40bcaf52150974a594459856","tid":1082651,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:00:22.000Z","msg":"要吳彥祖，金城武咁有型靚仔，180cm高<br />\n有份穩定工作，可能係政府工2a3o,紀律部隊officer 等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c7f4375972a7b30163c10660242aea1dbb47ba17","tid":1082651,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4614b575d02871fb40bcaf52150974a594459856","tid":1082651,"uid":205844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:00:22.000Z","msg":"要吳彥祖，金城武咁有型靚仔，180cm高<br />\n有份穩定工作，可能係政府工2a3o,紀律部隊officer 等等<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:00:46.000Z","msg":"因此呢家冇樓唔緊要<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d3e25a92d429828d0707358dc93445e50acec0c","tid":1082651,"uid":44562,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:06:22.000Z","msg":"梗係唔認同喇, 如果唔係咪一世唔使結"},{"pid":"be4ecdc7edb9b97f1abb5f3b0339894527c0533c","tid":1082651,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-29T09:06:57.000Z","msg":"緊係咁講，唔驚做老姑婆咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/n